Day 88: Ansible Blockinfile Module

Date: December 17, 2025
Overview
Modified configuration files by inserting blocks of text.
Key Concepts Learned

Blockinfile module
Markers for blocks
Idempotent file modification
Configuration management

Playbook
yaml- name: Add custom configuration
  blockinfile:
    path: /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf
    block: |
      <VirtualHost *:80>
        ServerName example.com
        DocumentRoot /var/www/html
      </VirtualHost>
    marker: "# {mark} ANSIBLE MANAGED BLOCK"

Challenges Faced
Ensuring blocks don't duplicate on multiple playbook runs.
